---
title: "US62 — Manage subscription access"
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor A as System Admin
  participant B as «Boundary»<br/>UsersScreen (detail)
  participant C as «Control»<br/>ManageSubscriptionAccess
  participant G as «Gateway»<br/>SupabaseGateway
  A->>B: open a user's subscription
  B->>C: grant / revoke premium
  C->>G: update subscriptions + profiles.role
  G-->>C: ok
  C-->>B: tier updated
  B-->>A: user's access level corrected
